{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water into mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket, weigh in shrimp and steam <b>12 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Cut steamed shrimp into pieces (¾ in.) and set aside. Clean mixing bowl.","Place cilantro leaves into mixing bowl and chop <b>4 sec\/speed 6<b>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside.","Place onion, chili and cucumber into mixing bowl and chop <b>6 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer into bowl with cilantro and set aside.","Place red snapper into mixing bowl and chop <b>10-12 sec\/speed 6<b>.","Add steamed shrimp, lime juice and salt and mix <b>5 sec\/\/speed 1<b>. Transfer into a bowl, cover with cling wrap and refrigerate for at least one hour.","Transfer chopped ingredients, fish and shrimp mixture, cherry tomatoes, mango and olive oil into a serving bowl and combine with spatula.","Season to taste and serve with crackers."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["18 oz water","10 ½ oz raw shrimp, peeled and deveined","½ oz fresh cilantro leaves","1 oz red onion","1 serrano chili, de-seeded and de-stemmed","5 oz cucumber, de-seeded and cut into chunks","11 oz red snapper fillets, boneless, skinless, semi-frozen, cut into pieces (1 in.)","7 oz freshly squeezed lime juice (approx. 14 limes)","¼ tsp salt, to taste","4 oz cherry tomatoes, halved","5 oz mango, diced (½ in.)","1 oz olive oil","ground black pepper, to taste","crackers, to serve"]}],"id":"r286472","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-DpLcngQSnVw\/XZMvmViBTiI\/AAAAAAAAaT8\/fwJV8w-XUJ0WFEGnaU7lMTdKZ2iBccf4ACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ktMGPIWK9cCQxBY4.png","title":"Ceviche","publishedAt":"2018-09-07T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"18 g","fat":"6 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"9 g","calories":"674 kJ \/ 161 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling wrap, serving bowl, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Replace raw shrimp with 10.5 oz cooked shrimp, clean and cut into pieces (¾ in.) and omit steaming of shrimp.","Make sure to always use the freshest ingredients. Consuming raw or undercooked meats, poultry, seafood, shellfish or eggs may increase your risk of foodborne illness."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 10m","6 portions"]}